# Detection Engineering Rules

## Definition of Done
Follow [[Detection Quality Bar]]:
- Intent, data source, logic, MITRE, validation, FP notes, response hints.

## IDs & Registry
- Assign `ES-DET-####`
- Register in [[Detections Index]]

## Linking
- Link to hunts and IR playbooks when outcomes require response.
- Map ATT&CK carefully via [[MITRE Mapping Guide]].

## Safety
- No unauthorized offensive payloads.
- Validation should be lab-safe and documented.
